version_description:
For QNB ALAHLI customers, you can now create your user and password through the application directly, changing your password from the application and login using fingerprint (for Supported devices only).

Also, you can add and manage other beneficiaries and transfers to them on click , secured with your m-token application.

In addition to new enhancements for transfers between your own accounts, cards and deposits.
